{"word":"H2449 - חָכַם - châkam - khaw-kam' - [idiom] exceeding - மிகவும்","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>חָכַם"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châkam"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-kam'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] exceeding / மிகவும்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஞானமடை, ஞானியாக்கு, உபாயம் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be wise"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to be or become wise, to act wisely"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to make wise, to teach wisdom, to instruet"},{"paragraph":"c) (Pual) to be made wise"},{"paragraph":"d) (Hiphil) to make wise"},{"paragraph":"e) (Hithpael) to show oneself wise, to deceive, to show one's wisdom"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root, to <i>be wise</i> (in mind, word or act): -  X exceeding, teach wisdom, be (make self, shew self) wise, deal (never so) wisely, make wiser."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2449 - חָכַם - châkam - khaw-kam'/2449\">H2449</a>, <a href=\"#/H2450 - חָכָם - châkâm - khaw-kawm'/2450\">H2450</a>, <a href=\"#/H2451 - חׇכְמָה - chokmâh - khok-maw'/2451\">H2451</a>, <a href=\"#/H2453 - חַכְמֹונִי - Chakmôwnîy - khak-mo-nee'/2453\">H2453</a>, <a href=\"#/H2454 - חׇכְמֹות - chokmôwth - khok-moth'/2454\">H2454</a>, <a href=\"#/H8461 - תַּחְכְּמֹנִי - Tachkᵉmônîy - takh-kem-o-nee'/8461\">H8461</a>"}]}